Mohan, lakukan sesuatu!

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:50.160
Bernapas.  Bernapas.  Tolong, sayang.

00:04:13.800 --> 00:04:14.800
Mama!

00:04:16.080 --> 00:04:17.560
Bu, tolong cepat!

00:04:19.520 --> 00:04:20.600
Mohan.

00:04:22.840 --> 00:04:23.800
Gungun...

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:25.160
Dimana obatnya?

